      "content": "i get that they're different frameworks, but in a real debate with a judge, one usually feels more 'correct' than the other. like, isn't it harder to justify trapping people in danger just to maintain a border? it feels like the humanitarian side has a much more objective moral high ground. wouldn't you agree?",
